{"tid":2164874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［中澳貿易戰］ 五糧液 VS 新世界！！","createTime":"2020-08-19T12:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T05:14:16.000Z","uid":45498,"like":66,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4c6d8af20ac774ee78985cccc6bd923ce2cd50","tid":2164874,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57MBzg6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57MBzg6.png&h=c77fc89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日各大澳洲頭版 <br />\n頭條內容大同小異 我攞咗其中一份<br />\n近乎全頁同支娜有關<br />\n最令鬼佬手足扯火嘅係貿易戰<br />\n中國威脅棄澳洲紅酒<br />\n<br />\n180cm FG月入50000連登仔<br />\n準備日日飲新世界紅酒未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRzMxaw_JApG4AAZRw6HOvCrXMvz-_vEtGs9g&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRzMxaw_JApG4AAZRw6HOvCrXMvz-_vEtGs9g%26usqp%3DCAU&h=500ba45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實掉返轉頭<br />\n澳洲地理條件咁撚屈機<br />\n無咩資源同產品一定要搵支娜買<br />\n鬼佬根本睇唔起啲垃圾支娜貨<br />\n<br />\n如果澳洲禁奶粉/牛奶/和牛出口去支娜<br />\n咁支娜仔咪大人細路都好撚肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRanBIX7fYwKIZjICxcP-HP0m2iVb1zoSFJKw&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRanBIX7fYwKIZjICxcP-HP0m2iVb1zoSFJKw%26usqp%3DCAU&h=bdd8b6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n介紹返 其實新世界係好高質<br />\n澳洲同紐西蘭天氣好<br />\n釀酒條件得天獨厚<br />\n例如Adelaide Hills 嘅地中海氣候<br />\n就盛產紅酒 <br />\n出名嘅酒莊地段就有 Barossa , McLaren Valley<br />\n當地紅酒業開荒全部係歐洲移民<br />\n你放心夠晒正宗 係法國同西班牙人主場<br />\n<br />\nAdelaide大學 Wine Science 排名世界第一 <br />\n見到澳洲紅酒減價 記得要掃吓貨喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你炒酒，新世界未必係好選擇 <br />\n但係又平又高質嘅餐酒<br />\n仲要鬼佬產地 去邊度搵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你點揀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開紅酒食和牛 撐澳洲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支娜的五糧液 世界的五糧液"},{"pid":"a62d95df93c6e0f6d2ab56518551927b4657d601","tid":2164874,"uid":55941,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"五糧液都係得班大老粗鄉下佬飲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39865a239538e26d82682e88a4c7f472b082484c","tid":2164874,"uid":339751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"五糧液？聽個名都知係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9477fbae6a994c32cbae11c18f54784fe12543","tid":2164874,"uid":45498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a62d95df93c6e0f6d2ab56518551927b4657d601","tid":2164874,"uid":55941,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"五糧液都係得班大老粗鄉下佬飲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"矛台 紹興<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cec17285bd18f4f292c50bf5337ed923b4c5795","tid":2164874,"uid":45498,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39865a239538e26d82682e88a4c7f472b082484c","tid":2164874,"uid":339751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"五糧液？聽個名都知係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTjFA9mh0jcJz4BdIOQ9NsNYZj9ibKp